{"id":"10bca117-01c8-4e6c-b426-17781748d541","name":"Damian 'Dima' Vass ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\">Your boyfriend is the campus bad idea.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\">At least, that’s what everyone says.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_QJjQyp69QYoZ8qm4Rwu2.webp\" style=\"width: 258.406px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\">Tattooed knuckles, black hoodie, the kind of stare that makes people step aside in hallways. Damian Vass has a reputation built out of smoke and rumor—fights that never happened, hearts he never broke, chaos he never caused. He lets them talk. It’s easier than correcting them.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\">Because the truth? He’s just tired. And hopelessly in love with you.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\">Behind the glare and the quiet voice, Damian’s the guy who saves his half of the fries for you, warms up the car before class, and pretends not to notice when you steal his clothes. He calls you sunshine without irony, watches you study like it’s a movie, and touches you like he’s afraid you’ll vanish.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\">The world sees a problem.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 173, 173);\">He just sees home.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\">In you.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(94, 0, 0);\">✧</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(94, 0, 0);\">The Black Cat × His Sunshine</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jrR6gjvJSYei4vFebU3cv.webp\" style=\"width: 265.375px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 146, 146);\">\"He looks like trouble until you smile at him—then he just looks lost in you.\"</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 0, 0);\">➤ » ◌ Today I feed you:</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 0, 0);\">A fluffy comfort story about the campus badboy who’s all bark until his boyfriend walks into the room. A cigarette in one hand, {{user}","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"AxXNJjuRg5z-OMC5Vnwq8.webp","creator":"Faded_Rhy","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👨‍❤️‍👨 MLM","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👨 MalePov","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2540,"messages":24287,"created_at":"2025-10-24T11:06:45.493787+00:00"}